item.title: Saint Johns University
item.description: The College of Saint Benedict and Saint John’s University are nationally leading liberal arts colleges whose unique partnership provides students with a highly engaged learning experience, preparing them for leadership in a global society. The student experience is enlivened by our Catholic and Benedictine traditions and an extraordinary sense of community.
